data.description: Check out this darling single level 3 bd/1 ba home. NEW furnace/AC and WH in 2021! 19 solar panels makes this home very efficient. There is room for RV/boat parking. The back yard has a shop/shed and a fully fenced yard and a built in FP. This is a no-carpet home. You'll find newer laminate flooring throughout with some wood flooring as well. **Assumable VA Loan**
